  "description": "<p>\n\t事情是这样的，小编在一家传统纸媒工作，今天要做大热的格莱美音乐颁奖典礼的专题，领导一脸无辜地告知，根据&ldquo;有关出版规定&rdquo;指示，文中所有人名、歌名、专辑名称都要翻译成中文&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p>\n\t内心真是一万只奥巴马在奔腾啊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/22beee3c10ae4d84ac276868b4cb2b20.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<span>这已经不是第一次遭遇如此要求了，最开始只是翻一两个人名、书名还没什么大碍，但越往后越丧心病狂，有些德文、俄文名字根本不会翻好嘛&mdash;&mdash;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<span>我的小伙伴咩咩在一次报道中提到一个德文的跨国公司，编辑说要翻成中文，咩咩说没法翻，那公司在中国注册名是什么四海物流公司之类的，很Low！</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<span>还记得iPad刚出那会儿，小记者们纷纷呐喊，是不是要翻译成苹果牌平板电脑才够彻底呢！</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/14d909f751e4469b9a112e7ab346d39e.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t所以要翻整个格莱美？拜托&hellip;&hellip;音乐专辑名翻成中文有多难，豆瓣网友已经示范过了&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n\t&lt;We Found Love&gt;（潍坊的爱）、&lt;Wake Me Up When September Ends&gt;（一觉睡到国庆节）、&lt;Hotel California&gt;（加州招待所）、&lt;Take Me Home Country Road&gt;（我回家走国道）什么的早就过时了！<br />\n\t以下这些才是高能预警&mdash;&mdash;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/5ef298f7ee144d9a910462150e38ed3b.gif\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t&lt;Belong&gt;&mdash;&mdash;碧浪<br />\n\t&lt;Love Maze&gt;&mdash;&mdash;辣妹子<br />\n\t&lt;Yesterday Once More&gt;&mdash;&mdash;耶稣他爹玩什么<br />\n\t&lt;I'm Just Going Down&gt;&mdash;&mdash;我就是够淫荡<br />\n\t&lt;Land of Pleasure&gt;&mdash;&mdash;东莞<br />\n\t&lt;One/Three&gt;&mdash;&mdash;万岁</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/c8b6b17953fb4e3080a012153a6a4f1e.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t&lt;Man on the Moon&gt;&mdash;&mdash;吴刚<br />\n\t&lt;Princess of China&gt;&mdash;&mdash;还珠格格<br />\n\t&lt;Where Have You Been&gt;&mdash;&mdash;威海油饼<br />\n\t&lt;Born This Way&gt;&mdash;&mdash;生育指南<br />\n\t&lt;Dangerous&gt;&mdash;&mdash;等着肉丝<br />\n\t&lt;Need You Now&gt;&mdash;&mdash;你就闹</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t&lt;Baby One More Time&gt;&mdash;&mdash;宝贝玩毛毯<br />\n\t&lt;Young Girls&gt;&mdash;&mdash;秧歌<br />\n\t&lt;Who's That Chick&gt;&mdash;&mdash;呼死那只鸡<br />\n\t&lt;Begnagrad&gt;&mdash;&mdash;别搁那嘎达<br />\n\t&lt;Diamond Mine&gt;&mdash;&mdash;呆萌的我</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t&lt;Harmony&gt;&mdash;&mdash;吓懵你<br />\n\t&lt;WonderWall&gt;&mdash;&mdash;弯的我<br />\n\t&lt;Flying in the Blue Sky&gt;&mdash;&mdash;蓝翔<br />\n\t&lt;当我出门总是下雨&gt;&mdash;&mdash;萧敬腾<br />\n\t&lt;Somebody That I Used to Know&gt;&mdash;&mdash;有些人，我用过才知道。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t真是&mdash;&mdash;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/e06fa6ce6ca94f0b9dca64359857f60a.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t说回本届格莱美，既然要翻，那么就翻！</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t翻译讲究信达雅：信就是忠于原文，达就是通顺，雅就是意境&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t我们的翻译原则，基本就一条，靠脑补&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n\t（鸣谢浩子、同兄、鲁鸽贡献脑洞）</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/982e1746ade4478894483cf789d4108d.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t年度专辑&lt;1989&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：你走不走！</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/a677ced506e342a7b97cb81de799cb8c.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t年度歌曲提名&lt;See You Again&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：西柚鹅肝</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/2e33d4d0bc66401fbd1509ea16d4cc01.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t年度专辑提名&lt;To Pimp a Butterfly&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：给蝴蝶拉个皮条</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/3fbe3f0440574608a5bc4fb1b390d6a5.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t年度制作提名&lt;Can't Feel my Face&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：早知道就不整容了</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/76844eb17026433194791ebd9a9f3eb2.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t最佳说唱专辑提名&lt;If You're Reading this Its Too Late &gt;<br />\n\t翻译：沙发没了！</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/2e5008d6be69445aad46058ca146a99e.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t最佳流行专辑提名&lt;How Big,How Blue,How Beautiful&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：重要的事情说三遍</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/7b991d1b2e3f4606a48d367ae561b85a.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t最佳流行专辑提名&lt;Piece by Piece&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：洋葱<br />\n\t（解释：我愿意一层一层地&hellip;&hellip;）</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/45cd2c633a384262951db46f23119cec.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t最佳流行专辑&lt;Uptown Funk&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：城中访客</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/a4d9f91bcc7841f1b08ee6d26da69f8d.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t最佳舞曲/电子专辑提名&lt;In Colour&gt;<br />\n\t翻译：茵佳妮&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n\t（国际大品牌）</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t看看，以上很多翻译虽然看上去有点神经，但除了超能音译部分外，大多翻译都做到了&ldquo;雅&rdquo;，也就是神似，这也是我们称之为&ldquo;神翻译&rdquo;的原因。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t接下来说点正经的，其实翻译真的是一件很严肃的事情，出版界有出版法规，翻译圈自然也有翻译规则，以及它的翻译门槛。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t歌，于我而言，是诗。<br />\n\t而诗歌翻译，是文学翻译中最讲究的一种。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t哪天，当我能够像徐志摩那样把Florence（佛罗伦萨）翻译成裴冷翠，像某些大神那样把Massachusetts（马萨诸塞州）翻译成满山秋色之时，我再把格莱美从头到尾翻个遍&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t你说好不好啊，领导？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/c0e3acc79fc447c0817afa716a00c381.gif\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本文系搞文艺授权沪江英语转载。本文仅代表作者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p766445/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p766445\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765014/\">测一测：你的语法拼得过7岁孩子吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766147/\">趣味漫画：单身狗的快乐生活 看完我笑了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766380/\">南极一座冰山倒了 15万只企鹅挂了……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766427/\">58届格莱美获奖金言：满满的励志感人正能量</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765144/\">穿衣露肉已经out啦！含蓄穿搭更显性感！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765231/\">2015年12月英语四级成绩查询时间公布！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766413/\">跟格莱美学英文：Thinking Out Loud笔记</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765835/\">职场宫心计：你怎么知道别人真的信任你？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766392/\">格莱美8大冷知识：啥？克林顿也拿过奖！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766235/\">BBC安乐死纪录片：死亡倒数 震撼百万观众</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
